{"tid":1203966,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好驚聽日返唔到工","createTime":"2019-06-11T13:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:59:38.000Z","uid":127532,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2998d0be3b83ba2a679feef4c98f5e8049c8c46c","tid":1203966,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:55:38.000Z","msg":"九巴職員權益工會呼籲車長 6．12 保持「安全車速行車」<br />\n九巴職員權益工會又指，為了市民的安全起見，呼籲各車長跟從公司《車長安全駕駛手冊》中的駕駛指引，叮囑車長：「時刻保持忍讓的專業精神，運用柔順的油針及逼力，確保乘客有舒適的乘車旅程；同時請謹記不論在市區或高速公路時，使用安全車速行車，盡量禮讓其他道路使用者；同時，作為守秩序的香港市民，請車長於進站時排隊，一架跟一架。以及將巴士停靠至站牌後，才可開啟前，後門讓乘客上落。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2374114/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%AC%8A%E7%9B%8A%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%206%EF%BC%8E12%20%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%9F%E8%A1%8C%E8%BB%8A%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2374114%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%259B%258A%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25206%25EF%25BC%258E12%2520%25E4%25BF%259D%25E6%258C%2581%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2580%259F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25BB%258A%25E3%2580%258D&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNdE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=4d59f49f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2374114/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%AC%8A%E7%9B%8A%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%206%EF%BC%8E12%20%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%9F%E8%A1%8C%E8%BB%8A%E3%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"2b1ddddf0c77b2ed3185b0ba3f7f2bb070e0ad60","tid":1203966,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"搭九巴返工既朋友點算"}]}